      "pubkey": "dW50cnVzdGVkIGNvbW1lbnQ6IG1pbmlzaW5pIHB1YmxpYyBrZXk6IEEzRTVGRTgwNjdBNEM4MjUKUldRbHlLUm5nUDdsbzdaZnhLajViVVp1Z1pGNk9ZRW95WkpVdk5DZXJ1Qi9tOUJvRkFKbVJmem8K",
      "endpoints": [
        "https://github.com/mc-werewolf/bds-launcher/releases/latest/download/latest.json"
      ],
      "windows": {
        "installMode": "passive"
      }
    }
  }
}
